%% Diagram: Saga compensation flow — happy path vs failure with backward recovery
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Orch as Orchestrator
    participant Inv as Inventory
    participant Pay as Payment
    participant Ship as Shipping

    Note over Client,Ship: Happy path
    Client->>Orch: PlaceOrder
    Orch->>Inv: ReserveItems
    Inv-->>Orch: Reserved
    Orch->>Pay: ChargeCard
    Pay-->>Orch: Charged (pivot)
    Orch->>Ship: CreateShipment
    Ship-->>Orch: Shipped
    Orch-->>Client: OrderConfirmed

    Note over Client,Ship: Failure: payment declined → backward recovery
    Client->>Orch: PlaceOrder
    Orch->>Inv: ReserveItems
    Inv-->>Orch: Reserved
    Orch->>Pay: ChargeCard
    Pay-->>Orch: Declined
    Orch->>Inv: ReleaseReservation (compensate)
    Inv-->>Orch: Released
    Orch-->>Client: OrderRejected
